Class BasicBeing

  • java.lang.Object
    • jig.Entity
      • Project2.BasicBeing
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Hero, Mob

    public class BasicBeing
extends Entity
    The BasicBeing class will define all HeroTypes and MobTypes this class defines all attributes heroes and enemies.

    • Constructor Detail

      • BasicBeing

        public BasicBeing(Vector screenPosition,
                  Vector worldPosition,
                  org.newdawn.slick.SpriteSheet walkingSheet,
                  org.newdawn.slick.SpriteSheet attackingSheet)
        Constructs a basic being by initializing its Screen and World position, current Animation, and next Vectors. The being gets initialized to the idle animation to begin with. Finally All the vectors for the next Being and map movement are initialized.
        Parameters:
        screenPosition: - A JIG Vector that set the Being starting location
        walkingSheet: - A sprite sheet of non attacking animation frames
        attackingSheet: - A sprite sheet of attack animation frames
